flowchart TB
    A[CI fails on master] --> B[CI Repair workflow\nfires via workflow_run]
    B --> C[curl POST to\nClaude API /run]
    C --> D[Remote routine\nwakes in Anthropic cloud]
    D --> E[Clone repo via\nClaude GitHub App]
    E --> F{Classify failure}
    F -->|fmt / clippy\ncompile / test| G[Fix source code]
    F -->|infra flake| H[Open GitHub issue]
    G --> I{Verify with\ncargo check or test}
    I -->|passes| J[git push origin master]
    I -->|fails| H
    J --> K[CI re-runs\non fix commit]

    style A fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff
    style K fill:#27ae60,color:#fff
    style H fill:#f39c12,color:#fff
    style J fill:#27ae60,color:#fff
